Package test

package test
This package contains all the test classes for the project. We use JUnit 5 to test the project. The test classes are in the same package as the classes they test. The test classes are named after the class they test, with "Test" appended to the end. For example, the test class for the class "LoginUI" is named "LoginUITest".
